            <img src="/images/about/yorushika.jpg" alt="Yorushika album cover" loading="lazy">
            <article class="caption">
              <h5>Yorushika</h5>
              <p style="font-size: 0.875rem">The song <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j83OVgv6woA&pp=ygUSbmF1dGlsdXMgeW9ydXNoaWth" target="_blank">"Nautilus"</a> is my favorite song during gap year 2020-21.</p>
            </article>
          </article>
          <article class="image-item">
            <img src="/images/about/cold-noodles.jpg" alt="Cold noodle with egg soup in Taipei" loading="lazy">
            <article class="caption">
              <h5>Cold noodles</h5>
              <p style="font-size: 0.875rem">My favorite cold noodle place in Taipei (<a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/Lx4DPW7ksU9CNHZy7" target="_blank">map</a>).</p>
            </article>     
          </article>
          <article class="image-item">
            <img src="/images/about/kenshi.jpg" alt="Kenshi Yonezu" loading="lazy">
            <article class="caption">
              <h5>Kenshi Yonezu</h5>
              <p style="font-size: 0.875rem">One of my favorite Japanese artists as well. (<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M2cckDmNLMI&pp=ygUJS0lDSyBCQUNL" target="_blank">KICK BACK</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9aJVr5tTTWk&pp=ygUKUEVBQ0UgU0lHTg%3D%3D" target="_blank">ピースサイン</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-tKVN2mAKRI&pp=ygUM5omT5LiK6Iqx54Gr" target="_blank">打上花火</a>)</p>
